I"d<p>HotspotBypass offers an easy way to change your MAC address on macOS. Get unlimited access to data-capped WiFi by randomizing your address everytime you run out of data or impersonate other network users and take theirs.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<h2 id="features">Features</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Change your MAC address</li>
  <li>See other MAC addresses in your current network</li>
  <li>Time your MAC address changes (e.g. change every 10 minutes)</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="disclaimer">Disclaimer</h4>

